platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Friendly competition with a like-minded sporting community is a big part of Stravas appeal. More than just a GPS, Strava shares your rides and runs automatically, so its low maintenance. See your rank on your favorite segment, join distance challenges, and follow your friends, pros, and even foes. As they say, If its not on Strava, it didnt happen.
